Package: geneOncoX
Type: Package
Title: Human gene annotations for the oncology domain
Version: 0.5.2
Date: 2022-09-21
Authors@R: person(given = "Sigve", family = "Nakken", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "sigven@ifi.uio.no",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8468-2050"))
Maintainer: Sigve Nakken <sigven@ifi.uio.no>
Description: A small collection of datasets relevant for gene annotations in the
    context of cancer. Datasets contain basic gene annotations, tumor suppressor,
    oncogene, driver gene annotations, as well as genes involved in cancer 
    predisposition. A collection of gene panels used in clinical cancer diagnostics
    are further provided.
URL: https://github.com/sigven/geneOncoX,
    https://sigven.github.io/geneOncoX/
BugReports: https://github.com/sigven/geneOncoX/issues
